Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.39,0:22:49.02,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}我们怀着同一个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.02,0:22:53.23,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a60}却以为彼此道路相左
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.23,0:22:56.52,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a60}让我们高举那被遗忘的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:22:59.28,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}踏荒野前行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.28,0:23:03.66,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a60}盈盈微笑 滚滚泪珠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.66,0:23:09.20,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a80}皆不可遗留于此地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.20,0:23:13.83,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}夏影倒映 白帜高扬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.83,0:23:21.30,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fax-0.2\4a60}那是你我的无名之旗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.30,0:23:26.80,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}在遥无尽头的道路彼端
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.80,0:23:30.10,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}那一线光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.10,0:23:31.93,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}牵动万千心绪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.93,0:23:35.81,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}深信头顶之青空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.81,0:23:41.03,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}启明星高悬东方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.03,0:23:43.57,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}为我们指引前路
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.57,0:23:50.58,ED CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3.5\fax-0.2\4a80}{\fad(0,800)}梦想必亲手实现
